{"tid":1767063,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講哂12月9係咪三罷","createTime":"2019-12-03T04:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T15:32:06.000Z","uid":2689,"like":34,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2601bf03fd3360fd440d7217451e816662c0fff5","tid":1767063,"uid":2689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"12月8就必定要行出黎<br />\n<br />\nSearch過有關12.9既post<br />\n好似冇乜討論就推緊12.9三罷<br />\n我見隔離post有人話係要keep住個勢<br />\n但依家有工會籌備緊行業罷工<br />\n三罷既方向應該點？<br />\n<br />\n我每次都有罷到<br />\n但一次比一次無力同灰<br />\n大公司大機構都冇乜人願意罷<br />\n唔開花既話<br />\n出面個世界好似如常一樣<br />\n<br />\n香港幾時先可以黎一次<br />\n真真正正既大三罷<br />\n市面可以一片死寂 死城一樣？<br />\n<br />\n唔好得少少人罷<br />\n然後最後要好多人衝然後拉哂"},{"pid":"374f40881f121d21766d50b9c58c603423772cdb","tid":1767063,"uid":130568,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"唔夠宣傳, 唔夠人罷黎有咩用?<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好再搞「被罷工」<br />\n塞鐵堵路唔係罷工，只係返唔到工<br />\n要罷就自己罷，自己罷唔到就認自私衰仔"},{"pid":"dcf9578b1dac853c2c3af5306547998eac305e79","tid":1767063,"uid":2689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9f99be79cd0cfa8de1ce139638edce42f2a33650","tid":1767063,"uid":2689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"64e52d0b8dbe497bbd3d44d8f3d98f6ab6092136","tid":1767063,"uid":2689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"df7cc06adbbe8f4a49675a2fa4546a38b57d7949","tid":1767063,"uid":245442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"癡人說夢"},{"pid":"4a74023ea62b782d5b43eee8bc1f4dbe93a1de2f","tid":1767063,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"374f40881f121d21766d50b9c58c603423772cdb","tid":1767063,"uid":130568,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"唔夠宣傳, 唔夠人罷黎有咩用?<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好再搞「被罷工」<br />\n塞鐵堵路唔係罷工，只係返唔到工<br />\n要罷就自己罷，自己罷唔到就認自私衰仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n<br />\n#2<br />\n遊物語<br />\n&bull;<br />\n21m<br />\n完全封鎖"},{"pid":"d275d6806901fb6494f35a0384e5f9df12975fe7","tid":1767063,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:02:11.000Z","msg":"三罷加黎明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8e597f39edfc132ce45a88c4861eb64354e490","tid":1767063,"uid":2689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"374f40881f121d21766d50b9c58c603423772cdb","tid":1767063,"uid":130568,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"唔夠宣傳, 唔夠人罷黎有咩用?<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好再搞「被罷工」<br />\n塞鐵堵路唔係罷工，只係返唔到工<br />\n要罷就自己罷，自己罷唔到就認自私衰仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"依家港豬進化左 <br />\n真係當打風咁好早出門口<br />\n參與人數越黎越少<br />\n盲推三罷我覺得唔樂觀<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都會罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔該真係三罷就比啲骨氣罷佢老母<br />\n唔得既就諗下仲有冇方法去完善個三罷<br />\n令更多人加入"},{"pid":"a7aa5f6653b3a35c677f409586b4d8b07688bc65","tid":1767063,"uid":217441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n12月8 維園見<br />\n12月9 黎明又來了"},{"pid":"f347b412bf2cb53fb1d895ca34503d9dc787b336","tid":1767063,"uid":2689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df7cc06adbbe8f4a49675a2fa4546a38b57d7949","tid":1767063,"uid":245442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"癡人說夢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"咁你有咩睇法？"},{"pid":"83983692564e6833c8fa3d990aecbabe92d6eb35","tid":1767063,"uid":238275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"「市面可以一片死寂 死城一樣？」有咩可能？ <br />\n<br />\n總有藍絲中立人係會生活如常"},{"pid":"865ca11a454ce4bbebd34215ab41c95562ab055c","tid":1767063,"uid":131122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,